        <mxCell id="p5-inset" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;5: Safety checks at CreateTaskFn&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;a.&lt;/b&gt; initial_approvals length ≤ 20 → else 400 VALIDATION_ERROR&#10;&lt;b&gt;b.&lt;/b&gt; each entry ≤ 128 chars → else 400&#10;&lt;b&gt;c.&lt;/b&gt; format parse: this_call | tool_type:X | bash_pattern:X | rule:X | all_session&#10;&lt;b&gt;d.&lt;/b&gt; for rule:&lt;id&gt; — REJECT if &lt;id&gt; is annotated @tier(&quot;hard&quot;)&#10;      (hard-deny rules can NEVER be pre-approved)&#10;&lt;b&gt;e.&lt;/b&gt; honor Blueprint security.maxPreApprovalScope ceiling&#10;      (e.g. max=tool_type_session rejects rule:X + all_session)&#10;&lt;b&gt;f.&lt;/b&gt; reject all_session if Blueprint prohibits it&#10;&lt;b&gt;g.&lt;/b&gt; approval_timeout_s ∈ [30, maxLifetime - 300]&#10;&#10;On any failure → 400/403 with {error, message, field}." vertex="1">
