        <mxCell id="p5-m16" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E8F5E9,#123318);strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;spacing=6;" value="[14:20:00]  ★ pre_approvals_loaded: count=2&#10;              scopes=[tool_type:Read, bash_pattern:git status*]" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="42" width="540" x="2280" y="1325" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-m17-note" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#999999;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;fontStyle=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=6;" value="... Agent starts running. Each tool call goes through PolicyEngine.evaluate_tool_use ..." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="800" x="400" y="1400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-m18" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1520" y="1460" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1520" y="1490" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-m18-box" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E3F2FD,#0d2638);strokeColor=#1F6FEB;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1F6FEB;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=6;" value="15: Tool call Read(&quot;README.md&quot;):&#10;    HARD_DENY eval → no match.&#10;    Allowlist fast-path: tool_type=Read ∈ allowlist → ALLOW (no soft-deny eval, no approval request).&#10;&#10;16: Tool call Bash(&quot;git status -sb&quot;):&#10;    HARD_DENY eval → no match.&#10;    Allowlist fast-path: bash_pattern &quot;git status*&quot; matches → ALLOW.&#10;&#10;17: Tool call Bash(&quot;git push --force origin main&quot;):&#10;    HARD_DENY eval → no match.&#10;    Allowlist fast-path → no match (neither tool_type:Bash nor bash_pattern match).&#10;    SOFT_DENY eval → force_push_any + force_push_main match → REQUIRE_APPROVAL → normal approval flow (see page 3)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="860" x="600" y="1500" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-cli-box" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-family:Helvetica;color:#555555&quot;&gt;Example CLI invocation&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;$ bgagent submit \&#10;    --repo my-org/my-app \&#10;    --task &quot;read the auth module and summarize&quot; \&#10;    --approval-timeout 600 \&#10;    --pre-approve tool_type:Read \&#10;    --pre-approve bash_pattern:&quot;git status*&quot;&#10;&#10;Submitted: 01KPW4X8M2QF...&#10;&#10;# watch the stream:&#10;$ bgagent watch 01KPW4X8M2QF..." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="460" x="20" y="1450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Why pre-approve?&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;· Declares security posture upfront — no mid-task interruptions for routine tools.&#10;· Maps to AI-DLC phased workflows (see §14.5): Phase 1 = reads only; Phase 2 = add docs writes; Phase 3 = all_session.&#10;· Safety net still present: hard-deny rules are NEVER short-circuited, even by all_session.&#10;· CLI validates scope format before hitting the API — fail fast, no wasted request.&#10;· CreateTaskFn is the enforcement boundary: rejects hard-deny rule pre-approvals, honors blueprint ceilings." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="700" x="2150" y="1500" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
