        <mxCell id="p6-t4-m3-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="16: bgagent approve ... --scope rule:write_infra_files" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="340" x="1130" y="1123" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t4-m4" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="830" y="1185" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="440" y="1185" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t4-m4-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="17: allowlist.add(&quot;rule:write_infra_files&quot;) → return allow" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="420" x="450" y="1163" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-hdr" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#EDE7F6,#1a1530);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=8;spacingLeft=12;" value="TURN 5 — later: any soft-deny triggers; user approves with --scope all_session" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="32" width="1400" x="90" y="1230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m1" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="130" y="1290" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="440" y="1290" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m1-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;" value="18: WebFetch(...) → REQUIRE_APPROVAL (webfetch_any rule)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="380" x="150" y="1268" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m2" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1410" y="1330" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1120" y="1330" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m2-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="19: bgagent approve ... --scope all_session --yes" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="340" x="1130" y="1308" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m3" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="830" y="1370" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="440" y="1370" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m3-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="20: allowlist._all_session = True → return allow" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="360" x="450" y="1348" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-t5-m4-box" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFEBEE,#3a1616);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#DD344C;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=8;" value="21: From now on: every SOFT_DENY → auto-ALLOW via allowlist._all_session check.&#10;    HARD_DENY still enforces (rm -rf /, .git/* writes, etc.) — _all_session has NO effect on hard-tier." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="820" x="200" y="1395" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-sidebar" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#1F6FEB;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1F6FEB;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Allowlist state after each step&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Initial (task start):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;{ all_session: false, tool_types: {}, rule_ids: {}, bash_patterns: [] }&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;After step 5 (scope=this_call):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;{ all_session: false, tool_types: {}, rule_ids: {}, bash_patterns: [] }&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;↑ unchanged — this_call is one-shot&lt;/span&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;After step 10 (scope=tool_type_session):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;{ all_session: false, tool_types: {Bash}, rule_ids: {}, bash_patterns: [] }&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;After step 17 (scope=rule:write_infra_files):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;{ all_session: false, tool_types: {Bash},&#10;  rule_ids: {write_infra_files}, bash_patterns: [] }&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;After step 20 (scope=all_session):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;{ all_session: true, ... }&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;↑ all_session=true short-circuits; other fields still tracked for diagnostics&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="500" width="520" x="1560" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-scope-ref" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Scope vocabulary&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;this_call&lt;/b&gt;&#10;  One-shot. Allowlist unchanged.&#10;  Next identical call re-prompts.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;tool_type:&lt;X&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (CLI: --scope tool_type_session)&#10;  Allowlist.tool_types.add(X)&#10;  All future tools of type X auto-approve&#10;  until container restart.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;bash_pattern:&lt;P&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&#10;  Allowlist.bash_patterns.append(P)&#10;  All future Bash cmds matching P (glob).&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;rule:&lt;ID&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&#10;  Allowlist.rule_ids.add(ID)&#10;  All future tools matching this soft-deny&#10;  rule auto-approve.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;all_session&lt;/b&gt;&#10;  Allowlist._all_session = True&#10;  Every soft-deny auto-approves. Hard-deny still enforced. Requires --yes on CLI." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="560" width="520" x="2100" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-notes" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Container lifecycle trade-off&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;The allowlist is held &lt;b&gt;in-process&lt;/b&gt; on the agent container (Python dict in PolicyEngine). It is LOST on container restart.&#10;&#10;Phase 3 accepts this trade-off because:&#10;  · AgentCore Runtime uses &quot;attach-don't-spawn&quot; — the same MicroVM is kept warm and reattached for nudges, watches, approve/deny traffic.&#10;  · maxLifetime = 8 hours — session is long-lived; the common case has ONE container for the whole task.&#10;  · Containers only restart on AgentCore-level failures (rare) or blueprint edits (require task restart anyway).&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Future work:&lt;/b&gt; persist allowlist to TaskTable (e.g. &lt;code&gt;effective_approvals&lt;/code&gt; attribute) so it survives container restarts. Not in Phase 3a. Phase 3b candidate if real-world usage shows escalation loss is a problem.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Hard-deny is unaffected.&lt;/b&gt; No scope — not even all_session — bypasses hard-tier Cedar rules. &lt;code&gt;rm -rf /&lt;/code&gt; still denies. &lt;code&gt;.git/**&lt;/code&gt; writes still deny." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="440" width="2000" x="90" y="1500" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p6-cli-ex" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-family:Helvetica;color:#555555&quot;&gt;CLI invocations across the task&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;# Turn 1&#10;$ bgagent approve 01KPW... 01KPR1... --scope this_call&#10;&#10;# Turn 2&#10;$ bgagent approve 01KPW... 01KPR2... --scope tool_type_session&#10;&#10;# Turn 3 — no CLI interaction (fast-path)&#10;&#10;# Turn 4&#10;$ bgagent approve 01KPW... 01KPR3... --scope rule:write_infra_files&#10;&#10;# Turn 5&#10;$ bgagent approve 01KPW... 01KPR4... --scope all_session --yes&#10;WARNING: all_session disables all approval gates.&#10;         Only hard-deny rules (rm -rf /, .git writes) remain." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="390" width="540" x="-457" y="836" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
