        <mxCell id="p7-e10-lbl" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#999999;" value="cancel / timeout / fail" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="140" x="777" y="201" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-forbidden" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFEBEE,#3a1616);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#DD344C;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;✗ NOT ALLOWED transitions&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;AWAITING_APPROVAL → COMPLETED (direct)&#10;AWAITING_APPROVAL → FAILED (direct)&#10;AWAITING_APPROVAL → TIMED_OUT (direct)&#10;AWAITING_APPROVAL → FINALIZING (direct)&#10;&#10;Terminal states are ALWAYS reached via RUNNING&#10;first. The hook returns to SDK, the agent&#10;processes the turn, then normal termination.&#10;&#10;Enforced by VALID_TRANSITIONS in task-status.ts:&#10;  AWAITING_APPROVAL: ['RUNNING', 'CANCELLED']&#10;(only two allowed target states)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="460" x="1248" y="125" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-orchestrator" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;arcSize=7;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;Annotations on AWAITING_APPROVAL&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Concurrency:&lt;/b&gt; holds the user's concurrency slot&#10;  (same as RUNNING). Docker container is alive,&#10;  AgentCore microVM still committed.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Orchestrator waitStrategy:&lt;/b&gt; treats as non-terminal,&#10;  continues polling TaskTable.status at 30s intervals.&#10;  (see orchestrate-task.ts)&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Reconcile-stranded-tasks:&lt;/b&gt; EXCLUDES AWAITING_APPROVAL&#10;  tasks. The task isn't stranded — it's waiting on a&#10;  human. Reconciler only fails tasks where no SSE&#10;  subscriber has attached for ≥300s.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Reconcile-concurrency:&lt;/b&gt; INCLUDES AWAITING_APPROVAL&#10;  in ACTIVE_STATUSES — counts against per-user cap.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;maxLifetime clock:&lt;/b&gt; keeps ticking during&#10;  AWAITING_APPROVAL. 8h absolute timer from session&#10;  start. approval_timeout_s ≤ maxLifetime - 300&#10;  (5-min cleanup margin enforced at submit time)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="460" width="369" x="1742" y="129" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-concurrency-ttl" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;" value="Concurrency example — Bob's story (per-user cap=10)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="900" x="100" y="800" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-concurrency-box" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=12;" value="t=0      Bob submits 10 tasks.   count=10.   11th submit → 429 (CONCURRENCY_LIMIT_EXCEEDED)&#10;&#10;t=2m     Task #1 hits soft-deny and moves to AWAITING_APPROVAL.   count still 10.&#10;         Bob's 12th submit → 429.   He can't add more until something frees a slot.&#10;&#10;t=30m    Bob approves task #1.   Task #1: AWAITING_APPROVAL → RUNNING.   count still 10.&#10;&#10;t=45m    Task #1 completes.   RUNNING → FINALIZING → COMPLETED.   count → 9.&#10;         Bob can now submit task #11.&#10;&#10;Takeaway: AWAITING_APPROVAL counts against concurrency — an unresponsive user can&#10;          starve their own slot pool. Either approve, cancel, or let timeout fire." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1800" x="100" y="840" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-legend" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999999&quot;&gt;● ━━━&lt;/span&gt; Existing (Phase 1/2)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;● ━━━&lt;/span&gt; ⚙️ Phase 3 addition&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;✗&lt;/span&gt; NOT ALLOWED transition&#10;&#10;Thick purple border = Phase 3 new state" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="180" width="440" x="1600" y="1140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-code" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-family:Helvetica;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;task-status.ts (abbreviated)&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;export const TASK_STATUSES = [&#10;  'SUBMITTED', 'HYDRATING', 'RUNNING',&#10;  'AWAITING_APPROVAL',  // NEW&#10;  'FINALIZING', 'COMPLETED', 'FAILED',&#10;  'CANCELLED', 'TIMED_OUT',&#10;] as const;&#10;&#10;export const ACTIVE_STATUSES = new Set([&#10;  'SUBMITTED', 'HYDRATING', 'RUNNING',&#10;  'AWAITING_APPROVAL', 'FINALIZING',&#10;]);&#10;&#10;export const VALID_TRANSITIONS = {&#10;  RUNNING: ['FINALIZING', 'CANCELLED',&#10;            'TIMED_OUT', 'FAILED',&#10;            'AWAITING_APPROVAL'],  // NEW&#10;  AWAITING_APPROVAL: ['RUNNING', 'CANCELLED'],&#10;};" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="460" width="540" x="-465" y="708" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p7-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Why hold the concurrency slot in AWAITING_APPROVAL?&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;Because the resource is still held. Container is alive. MicroVM is committed. Releasing the slot while the container lives would lie to the concurrency accounting and open a resource-exhaustion vector (user submits 1000 tasks, all go AWAITING, each holds a live container, slot count lies).&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Trade-off:&lt;/b&gt; an unresponsive user starves their own slot pool. Acceptable because: (1) the user opted in to the approval gate, (2) timeout always fires eventually, (3) `bgagent cancel` is always available. Future work: `bgagent approve --defer` to explicitly release the slot instead of silent timeout." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="1440" x="100" y="1160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="8. Cedar policy authoring guide" id="p3p8">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2820" dy="1430" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="3400" pageHeight="2400" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="p8-t" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=28;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;" value="Cedar policy authoring guide — hard-deny, soft-deny, and annotations" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="35" width="3300" x="40" y="25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-sub" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=13;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;" value="Reference page for Cedar policy authors. Hard-deny = absolute boundary. Soft-deny = REQUIRE_APPROVAL. Annotations carry metadata (rule_id, timeout, severity, category) that the engine merges on multi-match." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="3300" x="40" y="62" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-bar" parent="1" style="line;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;html=1;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="10" width="3300" x="40" y="105" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secA-ttl" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFEBEE,#3a1616);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#DD344C;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;spacingLeft=16;" value="A. Hard-deny examples (absolute — cannot be overridden)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="1580" x="60" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secA-code" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#0f0f0f);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=12;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;// hard_deny.cedar — file is parsed as @tier(&quot;hard&quot;)&lt;/span&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;hard&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;rm_slash&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.command &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*rm -rf /*&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;hard&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;write_git_internals&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;write_file&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.file_path &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;.git/*&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;hard&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;write_git_internals_nested&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;write_file&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.file_path &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*/.git/*&quot; };" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="360" width="1580" x="60" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secA-cap" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFEBEE,#3a1616);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=12;fontStyle=2;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#DD344C;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="These cannot be overridden by --pre-approve all_session or any other scope. Hard-tier policies always short-circuit at step 1 of evaluation (see page 2)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="1580" x="60" y="575" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secB-ttl" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#EDE7F6,#1a1530);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;spacingLeft=16;" value="B. Soft-deny examples (REQUIRE_APPROVAL — human in the loop)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="1580" x="60" y="660" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secB-code" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#0f0f0f);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=12;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;// soft_deny.cedar — file is parsed as @tier(&quot;soft&quot;)&lt;/span&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;force_push_any&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;300&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;medium&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;destructive&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.command &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*git push --force*&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;force_push_main&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;600&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;high&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;destructive&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.command &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*git push --force origin main*&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;write_env_files&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;600&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;high&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;filesystem&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;write_file&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.file_path &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*.env&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;write_infrastructure&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;900&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;high&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;filesystem&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;write_file&quot;, resource)&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.file_path &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;infrastructure/*&quot; };&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;webfetch_any&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;300&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;medium&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;network&quot;)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;invoke_tool&quot;,&#10;        resource == Agent::Tool::&quot;WebFetch&quot;);" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="456" width="1580" x="60" y="720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secB-cap" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#EDE7F6,#1a1530);strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=12;fontStyle=2;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="If multiple soft-deny rules match, timeout = min(timeouts) and severity = max(severities). Example: force-push to `origin main` matches both force_push_any (300s, medium) and force_push_main (600s, high) → resolved to 300s (min) + high (max)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="1580" x="60" y="1495" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-secC-ttl" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;spacingLeft=16;" value="C. Annotation reference" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="1560" x="1680" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-thead" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Annotation" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="320" x="1680" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-thead2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Required?" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="180" x="2000" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-thead3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Values" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="380" x="2180" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-thead4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2510);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#ED7100;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Purpose" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="680" x="2560" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r1-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="@rule_id(&quot;...&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="320" x="1680" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r1-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Yes on soft-deny" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="180" x="2000" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r1-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Unique across tiers (kebab or snake case)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="2180" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r1-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Stable ID for `--pre-approve rule:X` + audit trail" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="680" x="2560" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r2-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="@tier(&quot;...&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="320" x="1680" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r2-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Yes" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="180" x="2000" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r2-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="&quot;hard&quot; or &quot;soft&quot;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="2180" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r2-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Validates policy file placement. Engine rejects mismatch at load time." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="680" x="2560" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r3-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="@approval_timeout_s(&quot;N&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="320" x="1680" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r3-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="No" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="180" x="2000" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r3-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Integer seconds (e.g. &quot;300&quot;, &quot;600&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="2180" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r3-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="Per-rule override (soft-deny only). Default: task default. No effect on hard-tier." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="680" x="2560" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r4-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="@severity(&quot;...&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="320" x="1680" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r4-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="No" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="180" x="2000" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r4-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="&quot;low&quot;, &quot;medium&quot;, &quot;high&quot;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="2180" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r4-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#222222);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="CLI warning color (red/yellow/default). Default: &quot;medium&quot;." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="680" x="2560" y="420" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r5-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="@category(&quot;...&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="320" x="1680" y="480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r5-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="No" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="180" x="2000" y="480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r5-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="&quot;destructive&quot;, &quot;network&quot;, &quot;filesystem&quot;, &quot;auth&quot;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="2180" y="480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-r5-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" value="UX grouping. CLI could filter approvals by category. Not enforced." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="680" x="2560" y="480" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-gotchas" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;⚠️ Gotchas for policy authors&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;1. `like` is glob, NOT regex.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   Only `*` (zero-or-more) and `?` (exactly-one-char) wildcards.&#10;   If you need regex, write multiple `forbid` rules.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;2. Case-sensitive.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   `*rm -rf*` won't match `*Rm -Rf*`. Write both variants if case-insensitivity matters.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;3. For bash commands + file paths: use `context`, never `resource ==`.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   User-supplied values (command strings, file paths) go through the sentinel UID.&#10;   Always use `context.command` / `context.file_path` in the `when` clause.&#10;   Only `invoke_tool` matches on the real tool-name UID.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;4. `@rule_id` must be globally unique.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   Including across both tiers. `PolicyEngine.__init__` raises on duplicates.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;5. Hard-deny rules shouldn't have `@approval_timeout_s`.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   It has no effect. Engine warns but doesn't reject (compat if moved between tiers).&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;6. Blueprint cannot LOOSEN built-in hard-deny rules.&lt;/b&gt;&#10;   Per-repo blueprints can only ADD to the hard-deny set. The engine never allows&#10;   overriding or removing default hard-deny rules." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="381" width="470" x="20" y="560" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-blueprint" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FAFAFA,#0f0f0f);strokeColor=#01A88D;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;arcSize=5;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-family:Helvetica;color:#01A88D&quot;&gt;Per-repo customization via blueprint.yaml&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;# blueprint.yaml&lt;/span&gt;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;security&lt;/span&gt;:&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;cedarPolicies&lt;/span&gt;:&#10;    &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;hard&lt;/span&gt;: |&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;hard&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;block_prod_writes&quot;)&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal,&#10;              action == Agent::Action::&quot;write_file&quot;, resource)&#10;        &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.file_path &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;prod/**&quot; };&#10;    &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;soft&lt;/span&gt;: |&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@tier&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;soft&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@rule_id&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;deploy_staging&quot;)&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@approval_timeout_s&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;900&quot;)&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@severity&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;high&quot;) &lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;@category&lt;/span&gt;(&quot;destructive&quot;)&#10;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;forbid&lt;/span&gt; (principal,&#10;              action == Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;, resource)&#10;        &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; { context.command &lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;like&lt;/span&gt; &quot;*terraform apply*&quot; };&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;maxPreApprovalScope&lt;/span&gt;: &quot;tool_type_session&quot;&#10;  &lt;span style=&quot;color:#999&quot;&gt;# optional — caps what --pre-approve can grant&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="303" width="440" x="60" y="1620" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-merge" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E3F2FD,#0d2638);strokeColor=#1F6FEB;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1F6FEB;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Multi-match annotation merging&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;When Cedar returns ≥2 matching soft-deny rules, the engine merges their annotations:&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;timeout_s&lt;/b&gt; → &lt;b&gt;min&lt;/b&gt; (fail-faster wins)&#10;  Example: rules match at 300s + 600s → 300s&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;severity&lt;/b&gt; → &lt;b&gt;max&lt;/b&gt; (low &lt; medium &lt; high)&#10;  Example: medium + high → high&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;category&lt;/b&gt; → join with commas&#10;  Example: destructive + filesystem → &quot;destructive, filesystem&quot;&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;matching_rule_ids&lt;/b&gt; → union&#10;  User can pre-approve any of them via `--scope rule:X`&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Rationale:&lt;/b&gt; compound dangerous actions inherit the STRICTEST posture, not the laxest." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="300" width="1560" x="68" y="1186" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p8-legend" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF&quot;&gt;Syntax highlighting legend&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB;font-family:Courier New&quot;&gt;forbid, permit&lt;/span&gt; — Cedar keywords (blue)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#DD344C;font-family:Courier New&quot;&gt;when, like&lt;/span&gt; — conditional keywords (red)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#8C4FFF;font-family:Courier New&quot;&gt;@rule_id, @tier, @severity&lt;/span&gt; — annotations (purple)&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999999;font-family:Courier New&quot;&gt;// comments&lt;/span&gt; — explanatory (gray)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="334" x="545" y="1616" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="9. E2E scenario A — force-push w/ per-rule timeout" id="p3p9">
    <mxGraphModel dx="4834" dy="2451" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="3600" pageHeight="2800" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
