        <mxCell id="p9-m11" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF2E8,#3a2612);strokeColor=#ED7100;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;spacing=8;" value="11: PolicyEngine.evaluate_tool_use(Bash, {command:&quot;git push --force origin main&quot;})&#10;    a) HARD-DENY eval → no match → allowed&#10;    b) Allowlist check → empty → skip&#10;    c) SOFT-DENY eval → TWO rules match:&#10;       • `force_push_any`  @approval_timeout_s(300) @severity(medium)&#10;       • `force_push_main` @approval_timeout_s(600) @severity(high)&#10;    d) Annotation merge: timeout_s=min(300,600)=300, severity=max(medium,high)=high,&#10;       matching_rule_ids=[force_push_any, force_push_main]&#10;    e) Return: REQUIRE_APPROVAL(reason=&quot;Cedar soft-deny: force_push_any, force_push_main&quot;, timeout_s=300, severity=&quot;high&quot;)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="1280" x="1450" y="795" as="geometry" />
