        <mxCell id="p9-timeline" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E3F2FD,#0d2638);strokeColor=#1F6FEB;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;color:#1F6FEB;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;Wall-clock timeline (wait is real)&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;t=0.0s   submit POST /v1/tasks&#10;t=0.3s   201 task_id returned&#10;t=0.4s   stream open to Runtime-JWT&#10;t=3.0s   container ready, PolicyEngine loaded&#10;t=5.0s   rebase done, tests green&#10;t=6.2s   agent emits force-push Bash call&#10;t=6.21s  Cedar eval → REQUIRE_APPROVAL&#10;t=6.22s  PutItem TaskApprovalsTable&#10;t=6.23s  TaskTable → AWAITING_APPROVAL&#10;t=6.3s   SSE event reaches Terminal A&#10;t=6.3s   hook begins polling&#10;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#BF5700&quot;&gt;t=12s    user reads banner, decides&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#BF5700&quot;&gt;t=14.2s  user types approve command&lt;/b&gt;&#10;t=14.5s  POST approve returns 200&#10;t=14.5s  TaskApprovalsTable → APPROVED&#10;t=16s    hook's next poll reads APPROVED&#10;t=16.1s  allowlist updated, SDK gets ALLOW&#10;t=16.2s  git push executes (push takes ~2s)&#10;t=18.5s  next `git status` → fast-path&#10;t=22s    PR opened, task COMPLETED&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Approval wait: ~8s user-time, ~2s poll-latency&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="540" width="500" x="162" y="2134" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="YaQ0OxNv_JCSqRcu0lUm-2" edge="1" parent="1" style="endArrow=none;dashed=1;html=1;strokeColor=#C925D1;strokeWidth=1.5;" target="p9-inset" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1100" y="230" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1100" y="2700" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p9-inset" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-family:Helvetica;color:#BF5700;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;What Cedar saw at step 11 — three authorization queries&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999;font-family:Helvetica&quot;&gt;Query 1 (hard-deny policy set):&lt;/span&gt;&#10;  principal = Agent::Identity::&quot;agent-01KPR7...&quot;&#10;  action    = Agent::Action::&quot;invoke_tool&quot;&#10;  resource  = Agent::Tool::&quot;Bash&quot;&#10;  context   = { command: &quot;git push --force origin main&quot; }&#10;  →  Decision.Allow (no hard-deny rule matched)&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999;font-family:Helvetica&quot;&gt;Query 2 (soft-deny policy set, tool-name pass):&lt;/span&gt;&#10;  principal = Agent::Identity::&quot;agent-01KPR7...&quot;&#10;  action    = Agent::Action::&quot;invoke_tool&quot;&#10;  resource  = Agent::Tool::&quot;Bash&quot;&#10;  context   = { command: &quot;git push --force origin main&quot; }&#10;  →  Decision.Allow (tool-name alone doesn't trigger soft-deny; needs bash sentinel)&#10;&#10;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#999;font-family:Helvetica&quot;&gt;Query 3 (soft-deny policy set, bash sentinel pass):&lt;/span&gt;&#10;  principal = Agent::Identity::&quot;agent-01KPR7...&quot;&#10;  action    = Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;&#10;  resource  = Agent::BashCommand::&quot;command&quot;      &lt;span style=&quot;color:#BF5700;font-family:Helvetica&quot;&gt;← sentinel UID, same for all&lt;/span&gt;&#10;  context   = { command: &quot;git push --force origin main&quot; }&#10;  →  Decision.Deny (reasons: force_push_any, force_push_main)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="540" width="1500" x="732" y="2136" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
