        <mxCell id="p10-sub" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=13;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;" value="Hard-deny is NOT a friction point — it's a boundary. Agent attempts a DROP TABLE via Bash. Hard-deny rule `drop_table_any` matches → engine returns DENY immediately. No approval request is written. No state transition. No CLI prompt. The agent adapts its plan, retries with a different (safe) approach, and continues to completion. Sub-millisecond latency." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="3300" x="40" y="62" as="geometry" />
