        <mxCell id="p10-m10-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;fontStyle=1;" value="10: tool_use: Bash { command: &quot;psql -c \&quot;DELETE FROM test_users; VACUUM test_users;\&quot;&quot; }" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="500" x="430" y="948" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m11" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="420" y="1010" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1000" y="1010" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m11-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="11: SDK fires PreToolUse hook" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="260" x="500" y="988" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m12" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E8F5E9,#0f2f12);strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;spacing=8;" value="12: PolicyEngine.evaluate_tool_use:&#10;   a) HARD-DENY eval → context.command contains no &quot;DROP TABLE&quot; substring → no match → allowed&#10;   b) Allowlist check → not in allowlist → skip&#10;   c) SOFT-DENY eval → no rule against DELETE for this repo → no match → allowed&#10;   d) Return: ALLOW" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="1100" x="1020" y="1040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m13" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1000" y="1180" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="420" y="1180" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m13-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" value="13: return { permissionDecision: &quot;allow&quot; }" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="400" x="480" y="1158" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m14" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#555555;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#555555;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="420" y="1220" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="1870" y="1220" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m14-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;fontStyle=1;" value="14: SDK executes psql DELETE+VACUUM" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="400" x="800" y="1198" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m15" edge="1" parent="1" style="html=1;endArrow=classic;strokeColor=#555555;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontColor=#555555;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1870" y="1260" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="420" y="1260" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m15-l" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;fontStyle=1;" value="15: tool_result: DELETE 42; VACUUM" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="400" x="800" y="1238" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-m16" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#555555;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;spacing=6;" value="16: Task continues — agent opens PR, task COMPLETED. User in Terminal A only saw normal tool_use/tool_result events; the denied attempt appears as a regular &quot;permission denied&quot; tool_result (no approval banner)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1600" x="180" y="1300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-callout1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFEBEE,#3a1518);strokeColor=#DD344C;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px;color:#DD344C&quot;&gt;Key property: hard-deny is a BOUNDARY, not a friction point&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;User never sees a hard-deny. No prompt, no approval banner, no interrupted flow. The agent sees the denial in tool_result and adapts on its own.&#10;&#10;Hard-deny is for actions that are ALWAYS unsafe regardless of who asks:&#10;  • `rm -rf /` and friends&#10;  • writes to `.git/` or `.github/workflows/`&#10;  • schema-destructive DDL&#10;  • credential exfiltration patterns" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1040" x="60" y="1400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-callout2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#E3F2FD,#0d2638);strokeColor=#1F6FEB;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px;color:#1F6FEB&quot;&gt;No state transition to AWAITING_APPROVAL&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;Task stays in RUNNING. TaskTable unchanged. TaskApprovalsTable unchanged. Hard-deny latency: sub-millisecond — same as Phase 1a behavior.&#10;&#10;Compare to scenario A (soft-deny): two DDB writes + state transition + polling loop + user wait. Hard-deny short-circuits all of that." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1040" x="20" y="1400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p10-whatif" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFF9C4,#3a2e10);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=14;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:14px;color:#BF5700&quot;&gt;What if the user wanted DROP TABLE to be allowed?&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;The user CANNOT override a hard-deny rule via `--pre-approve` or any scope. Hard-deny is absolute (Decision #8 in §3).&#10;&#10;To allow DROP TABLE, the repo admin must MOVE the rule from the hard-deny tier to the soft-deny tier in `blueprint.yaml`:&#10;&#10;    security:&#10;      cedarPolicies:&#10;        soft: |&#10;          @tier(&quot;soft&quot;) @rule_id(&quot;drop_table_any&quot;)&#10;          @approval_timeout_s(&quot;900&quot;) @severity(&quot;high&quot;)&#10;          forbid (principal, action == Agent::Action::&quot;execute_bash&quot;, resource)&#10;            when { context.command like &quot;*DROP TABLE*&quot; };&#10;&#10;Now it becomes an approval gate — the user gets prompted, can approve with --scope. Task submissions cannot unilaterally bypass hard-deny." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="540" width="2100" x="60" y="1720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="11. E2E scenario C — --pre-approve all_session" id="p3p11">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1529" dy="903" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="3600" pageHeight="2600" math="0" shadow="0">
