        <mxCell id="p11-sub" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=13;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#555555;" value="Trusted terraform apply with full autonomy. User declares `--pre-approve all_session` at submit time. CLI prompts for confirmation (skippable with --yes). CreateTaskFn validates against the repo Blueprint's maxPreApprovalScope. Container starts with the allowlist pre-seeded. Every tool call hits the fast-path — ZERO approval gates fire. Hard-deny still enforces." vertex="1">
