        <mxCell id="p11-m2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#F5F5F5,#1a1a1a);strokeColor=#555555;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#111111,#E0E0E0);align=left;spacing=6;" value="2: CLI checks for --yes. Without it, prints warning (see inset) and waits on stdin. With --yes, skips prompt." vertex="1">
